Reylandt, Chairman Manh highly appreciated the Belgian 
Government and people's cooperation and assistance to the 
Vietnamese people over the past period. He expressed his wish 
that the fine traditional relations of friendship and 
cooperation between Vietnam and Belgium would be further 
developed. 
  In his reception of Albanian Ambassador Ferid Hoti, Chairman 
Manh thanked the Albanian people for their fine sentiments and 
precious support to Vietnam in its national defence and 
construction. 

