<H3> <TI>   Serbs Reportedly Fire Tank Shells at Tuzla </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Serbs Reportedly Fire Tank Shells at Tuzla </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   AU3105145094 Sarajevo Radio Bosnia-Herzegovina Network in 
Serbo-Croatian 1300 GMT 31 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> AU3105145094 </F>
<F P=104>  Sarajevo Radio Bosnia-Herzegovina Network </F>
<F P=105>  Serbo-Croatian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Excerpt] At about 1400 today, eight tank shells were 
fired on the broad region of the Dubrave airport [near Tuzla] 
from the chetnik positions in Citluk and (?Acino) Brdo. At that 
time a UN plane was landing on the runway. There is no 
information on the damage. This was reported by the Information 
Service of the 6th Operations Group Istok-Zivinice. [passage 
omitted] 

