<H3> <TI>   Foreign Minister Addresses Stability Conference </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Foreign Minister Addresses Stability Conference </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   AU0106112194 Bratislava SLOVENSKY DENNIK in Slovak 27 May 94 
p 3 </F>

<F P=103> AU0106112194 </F>
